      *  PRINT                                             *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C           #PRINT    BEGSR
      *
     C           LIN#      IFGE 66
     C                     EXCPT@HDR
     C                     Z-ADD3         LIN#
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ADD  1         SEQ#
     C                     EXCPT@DTL
     C                     ADD  1         LIN#
     C                     ADD  1         CNT
      *
